"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stick or get stuck, to cling or get caught","tags":["archaic"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to still do, to still be, to continue, not to cease","tags":["copulative","rare"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to meddle, to get involved in, to come to grips","tags":["archaic"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to break out, to occur (fire, war)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"attached, fixed"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to begin, to launch, to engage, to deal with","tags":["Yemen"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to yield, to produce, to grow","tags":["Yemen"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fortune, wealth, property; classy furniture","tags":["Yemen"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Denominal verb of نُشْبَة (nušba, “snare”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39779","headword_ar":"نَشَبٌ","root":"n$b","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"na$abapN","text_ar":"نَشَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano$abapN","text_ar":"مَنْشَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Moveable and immoveable property;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlN","text_ar":"مَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqaArN","text_ar":"عَقَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A'Obeyd, S, Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the latter only:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fixed property, consisting of animate and inanimate things;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"live stock and land &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land &c. with its live stock;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] lit. vocal and mute,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naATiq","text_ar":"نَاطِق"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAmit","text_ar":"صَامِت"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n$b","text_ar":"نشب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a term mostly applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immoveable property, such as houses and land;"},{"kind":"text","text":"whereas"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mAl","text_ar":"مال"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a term mostly applied to moveable property, such as silver and gold coin, &c.: but this latter term is sometimes applied to all that a man possesses; and sometimes especially, or particularly, to camels. (TA.) See also 8. [You say,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lkumo nasabN wamaA lakumo na$abN","text_ar":"لكُمْ نَسَبٌ وَمَا لَكُمْ نَشَبٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^anotumo A_il~aA xa$abN","text_ar":"مَا اَنْتُمْ اـِلَّا خَشَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ye have"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lineage; but ye have not fixed property: ye are nothing but logs of wood"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, and in a MS. copy of the K: in the CK, with the pron. of the third pers., and with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino","text_ar":"اـِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in place of the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA","text_ar":"ما"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"na$abN","text_ar":"نَشَبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain tree, of which bows are made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one of the trees of the desert."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Msb"]}]}}